\ round (nearest, half away from zero), round-up (ceil), round-down (floor),
\ truncate (toward zero). All polymorphic over floats and matrices.

\ ---- round ----
2.4 round .          \ 2
2.5 round .          \ 3
2.6 round .          \ 3
-2.4 round .         \ -2
-2.5 round .         \ -3
3.0 round .          \ 3

\ ---- round-up (ceil) ----
2.1 round-up .       \ 3
2.0 round-up .       \ 2
-2.9 round-up .      \ -2

\ ---- round-down (floor) ----
2.9 round-down .     \ 2
2.0 round-down .     \ 2
-2.1 round-down .    \ -3

\ ---- truncate (toward zero) ----
2.9 truncate .       \ 2
-2.9 truncate .      \ -2
-0.5 truncate .      \ 0

\ ---- polymorphic over matrices (element-wise) ----
[ 1.2 2.7 -1.5 -2.8 ] 2 2 matrix round .       \ [1 3 -2 -3]
[ 1.2 2.7 -1.5 ] 1 3 matrix round-up .         \ [2 3 -1]
[ 1.2 2.7 -1.5 ] 1 3 matrix round-down .       \ [1 2 -2]
[ 1.9 -1.9 ] 1 2 matrix truncate .             \ [1 -1]

\ ---- failure ----
"x" round
